{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_03_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 親友の本音",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインデー前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、おはようございます！\nレッスンを見に来てくれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good morning‚ {user}-san!\nDid you come to see my lessons?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、愛。そういえば、例のバレンタインイベント\nリズノワの出演が保留になってたけど……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Ai…Oh‚ the Valentine's Day event\nLizNoir appearance was put on hold. ……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すみません……それはまだ決まってなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry …… that hasn't been decided yet ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。今いるのは愛だけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Ai the only one there now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、なんだか落ち着かなくて……\n私だけ早く来ちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm kind of restless ……\nI'm the only one who came early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "体を動かせば、気もまぎれるかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it would help to move my body and take my mind off things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんだか様子がおかしいな）\n（バレンタインイベントのことで何かあったのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…… Something's not right here.）\n（What's up with the whole Valentine's Day event thing?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "愛、悩みごとがあるなら、相談してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ if you have a problem‚ why don't you talk to me about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、これは私達LizNoirの問題なので\n{user}さんに頼るのも悪いかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… but this is a problem for us at LizNoir.\nso I felt bad relying on {user}-san …….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ。それに、当事者じゃないからこそ\n言えるアドバイスだってあるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. Besides‚\nthere might be some advice that I can give you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれません……\nじゃあ、相談に乗ってもらってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might be right…\nThen‚ can you listen to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……他の人がいる所だと、ちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ but …… where others are not around ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあレッスンが終わったら俺に連絡してくれ\n事務所のそばの喫茶店で落ち合おう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then call me when you're done with your lesson.\nMeet me at the coffee shop by the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n……{user}さん、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I Understood.\nThank you‚ ……{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 83.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 83.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こころが……変？\nちょっとユニークな子だとは思っていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro is …… strange?\nI knew she was a bit unique‚ but ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとどころじゃないですよ\nこころはかなり変わった子で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just a little bit.\nKokoro is a very strange girl…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 96.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "――って、何言わせるんですか！　もう！\nそうじゃなくてですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Why did you make me say that?!　Oh‚ God!\nThat's not what I meant. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん。やっと調子が出てきたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. You're finally getting better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 106.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\n……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah……\nThank you ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それでどう変なんだ？　何か心当たりでも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what's weird about it?　Do you have any idea what's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……それがですね\nバレンタインイベントの話が出た頃からなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm …… that's it.\nIt all started around the time we started talking about the Valentine's Day event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、レッスンと食事の時以外は\nずっと部屋にこもってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since then‚ she's been holed up\nin her room except for lessons and meals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインイベントに向けて\n新曲の構想を練ってるみたいなんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think she is working on\na new song idea for the Valentine's Day event……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 135.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。イベントへの参加の返事を\n保留にしていた理由、もしかしてそれなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't realize that. Could that be the reason\nwhy you were holding off on responding to the event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お待たせしてすみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ sorry to keep you waiting ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 147.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワがイベントに出るかどうかは\nこころのアイデア次第っていうことになっていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was decided that whether or not LizNoir would be\nat the event would depend on Kokoro's idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "私も手伝ってはいますけど……\nこころは怖いくらいに必死なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm helping‚ though ……\nKokoro is frighteningly desperate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 161.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 164.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか痛々しいくらいに……\n寝言でうなされてることもあったんです",
